## PaymentRecord Model

```python
class PaymentRecord:
    id: int
    order_id: int | None          # set after order creation
    checkout_session_id: int
    stripe_payment_intent_id: str  # unique
    stripe_charge_id: str | None
    amount: Decimal
    currency: str
    status: str  # pending | processing | succeeded | failed | cancelled | refunded
    idempotency_key: str           # unique
    failure_code: str | None
    failure_message: str | None
    payment_method_summary: dict | None  # {brand, last4, exp_month, exp_year}
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: datetime
```

